<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>404 Page Not Found</title>
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.6.0/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-Kc323vGBEqzTmouAECnVceyQqyqdsSiqLQISBL29aUW4U/M7pSPA/gEUZQqv1cwx4OnYxTxve5UMg5GT6L4JJg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">

<style>
    body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px;
    background-color: #f8f9fa;
    }
    .error {
    font-size: 150px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: white;
    filter: drop-shadow(2px 2px 2px #779ecb);
    }
    .error-icon {
    font-size: 60px;
    color: #779ecb;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    h1 {
    font-size: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    color: #779ecb;
    }
    p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #6c757d;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
    }
    .btn-home {
    font-size: 16px;
    background-color: #779ecb;
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 25px;
    text-decoration: none;
    }
    .btn-home:hover {
    background-color: #779ecb;
    color: white;
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <div class="error-icon" style="margin-bottom: -40px;">
    <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle" style="font-size: 90px;"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="error">404</div>
    <h1>Page Not Found</h1>
    <p>We're sorry, please contact the administrator for your concern or just read out terms and conditions. Thank you.</p>

    <!-- Return button that navigates back to the previous page -->
    <button class="btn-home" onclick="window.history.back();" style="border: none;">Return</button>

</div>

</body>
</html>
